# ForgeAI Design System v6

Reference design: `/assets/Screenshot_2026-03-07_at_11.43.53-205d57af-dd94-47af-a45e-cc683ba74ad2.png`
Full spec: `DESIGN_SYSTEM.md` at project root.

## Stack

- Tailwind CSS v4 (`@theme` in `globals.css`, no config file)
- Radix UI primitives (Dialog, DropdownMenu, ScrollArea, Separator, Tooltip)
- Phosphor Icons (`@phosphor-icons/react`) for workspace, Lucide for landing
- `class-variance-authority` + `clsx` + `tailwind-merge` for variant composition
- `next-themes` with class strategy (light/dark/system)
- `motion` for animations

## Color Tokens — "Technical Light"

Cool neutral grayscale base with high-chroma semantic accents.
Use CSS variables via Tailwind classes (e.g. `bg-forge-bg`, `text-forge-text`).

### Backgrounds

| Token                  | Light            | Dark            | Usage                       |
|------------------------|------------------|-----------------|-----------------------------|
| `--color-forge-bg`     | `#F8F9FA`        | `#0a0a0a`       | App background (cool neutral)|
| `--color-forge-surface`| `#ffffff`        | `#141414`       | Cards, panels, modals       |
| `--color-forge-surface-2`| `#F1F3F5`     | `#1e1e1e`       | Toolbars, nested inputs     |

### Text

| Token                        | Light      | Dark       |
|------------------------------|------------|------------|
| `--color-forge-text`         | `#212529`  | `#ececec`  |
| `--color-forge-text-secondary`| `#495057` | `#a3a3a3`  |
| `--color-forge-text-dim`     | `#868E96`  | `#888888`  |

### Borders

| Token                        | Light                    | Dark                        |
|------------------------------|--------------------------|-----------------------------|
| `--color-forge-border`       | `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08)`   | `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12)` |
| `--color-forge-border-subtle`| `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)`   | `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08)` |

