## Typography

Font: **Inter** via `next/font/google` (`--font-inter`).

| Role             | Size    | Weight   | Tracking     | Transform  |
|------------------|---------|----------|--------------|------------|
| Logo "FORGE AI"  | `16px`  | `700`    | `0.08em`     | `uppercase`|
| Nav link         | `14px`  | `500`    | `-0.01em`    | —          |
| Section header   | `11px`  | `600`    | `0.06em`     | `uppercase`|
| Card title       | `14px`  | `600`    | `-0.01em`    | —          |
| Card body        | `13px`  | `400`    | `-0.005em`   | —          |
| Meta/dates       | `12px`  | `400`    | `0`          | —          |
| Badge label      | `12px`  | `600`    | `0`          | —          |
| Caption/helper   | `11px`  | `400`    | `0`          | —          |

## Spacing: 16–20px padding inside cards/sidebar items. Card grid gap: 16px.

## Border Radius

| Element          | Radius          | Tailwind class   |
|------------------|-----------------|------------------|
| Cards            | `12–16px`       | `rounded-xl`     |
| Status badges    | `9999px`        | `rounded-full`   |
| Buttons          | `8px`           | `rounded-lg`     |
| Avatars          | `9999px`        | `rounded-full`   |
| Dropdown menus   | `12px`          | `rounded-xl`     |
| Floating toolbar | `9999px`        | `rounded-full`   |

## Shadows

```css
--shadow-card: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);      /* soft wide spread */
--shadow-panel: 0 1px 2px rgba(15,23,42,0.06), 0 10px 28px rgba(15,23,42,0.10);
--shadow-dropdown: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08), 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
```

