## Component Patterns

### Status Badge (PASTEL pill, dark text)

```tsx
<span className={cn(
  "inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold",
  status === "running" && "bg-status-running text-forge-text",
  status === "inactive" && "bg-status-inactive text-forge-text",
  status === "overdue" && "bg-status-overdue text-forge-text",
  status === "done" && "bg-status-done text-forge-text",
)}>
  {label} <ChevronDown size={12} />
</span>
```

### Card (Task/Project)

```tsx
<div className="bg-forge-surface rounded-xl shadow-card p-4 border border-forge-border-subtle">
  <div className="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
    <span className="text-xs font-medium text-forge-amber">Team 1</span>
    <StatusBadge status="running" />
  </div>
  <h3 className="text-sm font-semibold text-forge-text mb-1">{title}</h3>
  <p className="text-[13px] text-forge-text-secondary line-clamp-2">{description}</p>
  <div className="flex items-center justify-between mt-3 text-xs text-forge-text-dim">
    <span>Due: {date}</span>
    <AvatarStack users={assignees} />
  </div>
</div>
```

### Sidebar Tree Item

```tsx
<button className={cn(
  "w-full flex items-center gap-2.5 px-2.5 py-2 rounded-lg text-[13px] transition-colors",
  isSelected
    ? "bg-forge-amber-bg text-forge-text font-medium"
    : "text-forge-text-secondary hover:bg-black/[0.03]"
)}>
```

### Bottom Floating Toolbar

```tsx
<div className="fixed bottom-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-40 glass rounded-full px-2 py-1.5 flex items-center gap-1 shadow-panel">
  {tools.map(tool => <IconButton key={tool.id} ... />)}
</div>
```

## Conventions

- Prefer CSS variables via Tailwind classes over inline `style={{ }}` props
- Use `cn()` from `clsx`/`tailwind-merge` for conditional classes
- All interactive elements: `cursor-pointer`, visible focus ring
- File naming: kebab-case for files, PascalCase for components
- Icons: Phosphor for workspace (size 16-18), Lucide for landing (size 20-24)
